Primeface

Primeface is a page where we keep all common components or widgets related to TravelNXT themes.

Purpose of using Primeface

The main purpose of using primeface is that by the help of this page we can see all the internal pages related to any theme at one single page. So, that if next time any theme comes up, user can easily modify the changes on one particular page by just applying the theme and the page gets rendered.

Advantages of using Primeface

  • The main advantage of using this page is that much time is reduced in navigating the whole pages.
  • Second advantage is that user can easily make use of common components related to TravelNXT product.

Base

The Base page is used to refer the most common elements of the theme.

Profile

Default theme is using Google's Lato font family. No any other font family is used.

The Google font API is linked in the Master Page head section and the font family is mentioned in the "core-style.css".

Google Font API

‹link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:400,100,100italic,300,300italic,400italic,500,500italic,700,700italic,900,900italic' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'›

If in case you need to implement any new font family you need the font API as above with different font weights eg. 400, 600, 700 etc.
